<paragraph id="HF9D811B97B5B4B46A11794D2C4A29622"><enum>(19)</enum><text display-inline="yes-display-inline">Other authorities as appropriate.</text></paragraph></subsection> <subsection id="H3BE21926220741F6AB21FCF250B92786"><enum>(b)</enum><header>Content</header><text display-inline="yes-display-inline">The report shall detail the following:</text>
